messages.propos3: In fact, we reduce our responsibility to a minimum through our work,In fact, we reduce our responsibility to a minimum through our work,In fact, we reduce our responsibility to a minimum through our work, unless we are on leave to exercise it. The suffering we endure entitles us to blame with very little pleasure, except that nothing happens
